                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">汉尼拔会死，但罗马人生生不息</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="970141035">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-970141035" class="vote-count">9</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-970141035" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="970141035">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/diaoduoxi/">diaoduoxi</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-10-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">第二部要义：汉尼拔以一己之力，破罗马十万之众，纵横十六载，战无不胜，实前所未有之劲敌。然胜者不能服，败者不言弃，持久战之滥觞盖始于此。费边之持重，马尔凯鲁斯之至勇，尼禄之果敢，罗马同盟之忠诚积胜于前，而西庇阿毕其功于扎马。此非天命哉？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

